rld%2Fus%2Fmore-than-a-foot-of-snow-100-mph-wind-gusts-possible-as-storm-approaches-sierra-nevada%2Famp_articleshow%2F105335031.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmore-than-a-foot-of-snow-100-mph-wind-gusts-possible-as-storm-approaches-sierra-nevada%2Famp_articleshow%2F105335031.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unidentified%20Flying%20Object%20Near%20Imphal%20Airport%2C%202%20Flights%20Diverted%2C%203%20Delayed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20flights%20in%20Imphal%20airport%20sat%20on%20the%20tarmac%20for%20over%20three%20hours%20and%20two%20incoming%20flights%20took%20a%20diversion%20towards%20Kolkata%20and%20Guwahati%20after%20the%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20reported%20an%20unidentified%20flying%20object%20near%20the%20runaway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20authorities%20immediately%20closed%20the%20%26quot%3Bcontrolled%20airspace%26quot%3B%20in%20Manipur's%20capital%20Imphal%20and%20stopped%20all%20flight%20operations.%20Some%201%2C000%20passengers%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20airspace%20closure%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(AAI)%20handed%20over%20the%20airspace%20control%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20before%20the%20IAF%20gave%20the%20all-clear%20to%20restore%20the%20airspace%20for%20commercial%20flight%20operations%2C%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20NDTV%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20traffic%20control%20(ATC)%20and%20people%20on%20the%20ground%20saw%20the%20drones%20around%202%20pm%2C%20after%20which%20the%20three%20flights%20-%20two%20Air%20India%2C%20and%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20-%20were%20told%20not%20to%20take%20off%2C%20sources%20said.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20two%20incoming%20flights%20were%20diverted%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20was%20seen%20as%20disturbing%20amid%20the%20tension%20in%20Manipur%20following%20months%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%20Several%20groups%20had%20used%20drones%20during%20the%20violence.%20In%20neighbouring%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20junta%20forces%20have%20been%20launching%20airstrikes%20against%20Chin%20State%20rebels%20along%20the%20border%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ffakud6r_imphal-airport_625x300_19_November_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flights%20that%20had%20been%20diverted%20are%20likely%20to%20reach%20Imphal%20tonight%20as%20the%20airport%20-%20although%20surrounded%20by%20hills%20-%20has%20night-landing%20capability.%20The%20flights%20which%20were%20diverted%20will%20be%20operated%20today%20as%20watch%20hours%20have%20been%20extended%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImphal%20airport%20director%20Chipemmi%20Keishing%20in%20a%20statement%20confirmed%20the%20sighting%20of%20the%20drone.%20The%20officer%20said%20all%20the%20three%20flights%20took%20off%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bcompetent%20authority%26quot%3B%20gave%20security%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassengers%20told%20NDTV%20many%20of%20them%20had%20been%20inside%20the%20airport%20and%20some%20inside%20the%20aircraft%20for%20over%20three%20hours%20from%203%20pm%2C%20until%20the%20flights%20took%20off%20one%20after%20another%20around%206.15%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoarding%20was%20completed%20by%203%20pm%2C%20but%20we%20finally%20got%20the%20take-off%20clearance%20at%206.10%20pm.%20Passengers%20were%20worried%20and%20some%20elderly%20people%20anxious%2C%20but%20everyone%20was%20extremely%20cooperative%20and%20patient%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20woman%20who%20boarded%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20to%20Delhi%20told%20NDTV%20on%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20passenger%