in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnigeria-frees-4000-prisoners-to-ease-jail-crowding%2Farticleshow%2F105334761.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnigeria-frees-4000-prisoners-to-ease-jail-crowding%2Famp_articleshow%2F105334761.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fnigeria-frees-4000-prisoners-to-ease-jail-crowding%2Famp_articleshow%2F105334761.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Cup%20Final%3A%20How%20Australia%20Managed%20To%20Dominate%20In-Form%20Indian%20Batters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20grizzly-haired%20veterans%20brought%20all%20their%20big-game%20experience%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20restricting%20a%20hitherto%20rollicking%20India%20to%20240%20all%20out%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Sunday.%20Their%20dominance%20over%20the%20hosts%20had%20multiple%20focal%20points%20to%20it%2C%20while%20India%20made%20a%20couple%20of%20moments%20of%20their%20own%20through%20fifties%20by%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20KL%20Rahul.%20Here's%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20important%20moments%20in%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%20lives%20by%20sword%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20Rohit%20batted%20only%20in%20one%20gear%2C%20evidenced%20by%20his%20strike-rate%20of%20126.%20On%20this%20day%2C%20the%20Mumbaikar%20made%20runs%20at%20151.%20His%20strategy%20was%20clear%2C%20blunt%20the%20Aussie%20new%20ball%20bowlers%20and%20the%20skipper%20blasted%20two%20sixes%20off%20pacer%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20to%20give%20early%20momentum%20to%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Rohit's%20innings%20did%20not%20bloom%20into%20something%20bigger.%20His%20effort%20to%20hoist%20off-spinner%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20over%20the%20ring%20ended%20when%20Travis%20Head%20took%20a%20lovely%20running-diving%20catch%20towards%20sweeper%20cover.%20Australia%20snapped%20India's%20march%20too%20for%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAustralia's%20fielding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Antipodeans%20have%20always%20been%20a%20very%20good%20fielding%20side%2C%20and%20they%20raised%20the%20bar%20one%20notch%20up%20in%20the%20summit%20clash.%20Travis%20Head%20took%20that%20brilliant%20running%20catch%20to%20dismiss%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20David%20Warner%20made%20more%20than%20one%20diving%20saves%20near%20the%20ropes%20to%20save%20the%20boundaries%2C%20leaving%20Indian%20batters%20a%20bit%20frustrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20forced%20them%20to%20change%20their%20gung-ho%20approach%20that%20they%20followed%20so%20far%20in%20the%20tournament.%20Cummins%20also%20made%20some%20really%20good%20field%20placements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kohli%20and%20Rahul%20were%20batting%2C%20the%20Aussies%20skipper%20opened%20the%20cover%20region%20with%20a%20sweeper%20in%20place%20and%20closed%20ranks%20around%20the%20square-leg%20and%20mid-on%20areas.%20It%20was%20a%20clear%20ploy%20to%20force%20the%20Indian%20batters%20to%20take%20more%20risks%20to%20make%20quick%20runs%2C%20or%20contend%20with%20those%20workman-like%20singles%20to%20covers%20and%20leg-side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEdgy%20Gill%20and%20Shreyas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20final%20for%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20and%20they%20looked%20a%20bit%20nervous.%20Gill%20was%20like%20a%20cat%20on%20a%20hot%20tin%20roof%2C%20and%20hardly%20offered%20a%20settled%20moment.%20His%20harrowing%20time%20at%20crease%20ended%20when%20a%20half-hearted%20pull%20off%20left-arm%20pacer%20Mitchell%20Starc%20found%20Adam%20Zampa%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20came%20to%20this%20match%20riding%20on%20back-to-back%20hundreds%20against%20Netherlands%20and%20New%20Zealand.%20But%20this%20noon%2C%20his%20innings%20lasted%20just%20three%20balls.%20Cummins%20caught%20him%20rooted%20inside%20the%20crease%20with%20a%20delivery%20that%20jagged%20back%20just%20enough%20at%20a%20fair%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKohli%20and%20Rahul%20stand%20tall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20joined%20forces%20when%20India%20were%20shaking%20at%2081%20for%203%2C%20but%20Kohli%20and%20Rahul%20sussed%20up%20the%20conditions%20and%20pitch%20very%20well%2C%20knuckled%20down%20to%20make%20steadying%2067%20runs%20for%20the%20fourth%20wicket.%20It%20was%20more%20industrious%20than%20eye-popping%2C%20but%20that%20was%20what%20India%20needed%20at%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20entire%20alliance%20had%20just%20one%20boundary%20in%20it%2C%20but%20India%20recovered%20to%20a%20good%20extend%20through%20them%20until%20Kohli%20(54)%20chopped%20one%20from%20Pat%20Cummins%20onto%20his%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rahul%20(66)%20continued%20to%20hold%20the%20innings%20together%20with%20a%20composed%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaptain%20Cummins%20and%20his%20bowlers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20whole%20of%20this%20showpiece%20Pat%20Cummins%20the%20bowler%20was%20conspicuous%20by%20his%20absence.%20Coming%20into%20this%20match%2C%20the%20pacer's%20run-rate%20was%20above%20six%20and%20has%20taken%2013%20wickets%20from%2010%20matches.%20But%20he%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20make%20a%20bigger%20impact%2C%20and%20the%20New%20South%20Welshman%20chose%20the%20finest%20occasion%20to%20make%20his%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20got%20the%20big%20wickets%20of%20in-form%20Kohli%20and%20Shreyas%20to%20keep%20India%20in%20check%2C%20also%20bowled%20an%20economic%20spell.%20Pacers%20Mitchell%20Starc%20and%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20too%20helped%20him%20taking%20five%20wickets%20among%20them%20on%20a%20pitch%20that%20had%20very%20little%20for%20their%20type%20of%20bowlers%2C%20using%20umpteen%20variations.%20The%20spinners%20--%20Adam%20Zampa%2C%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20and%20Travis%20Head%20--%20too%20chipped%20in%20choking%20run-flow%20in%20the%20middle%20period.%20They%20hardly%20allowed%20Indians%20to%20get%20the%20boundaries%2C%20a%20vital%20part%20of%20India's%20batting%20supremacy%20in%20the%20tournament%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20two%20periods%20of%20prolonged%20boundary%20drought%20in%20hosts'%20innings%2C%20the%20Rahul-Kohli%20stand%20where%20India%20managed%20a%20lone%20four%2C%20and%20in%20the%20period%20between%2041st%20and%2050th%20overs%2C%20a%20phase%20when%20India%20managed%20just%20two%20fours%20through%20Mohammed%20Shami%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700401260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fuavo8o08_australia-afp_625x300_19_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fworld-cup-final-how-australia-managed-to-dominate-in-form-indian-batters-4587375%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20Australia%20bowlers%20kept%20India%20under%20the%20pump%2C%20the%20hosts%20made%20a%20couple%20of%20moments%20of%20their%20own%20through%20fifties%20by%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20KL%20Rahul.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fworld-cup-final-how-australia-managed-to-dominate-in-form-indian-batters-4587375%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fworld-cup-final-how-australia-managed-to-dominate-in-form-indian-batters-4587375%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.