stributed%20by%20the%20Agarwal%20Medical%20Centre%20employees%20in%20Sangam%20Vihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%20they%20arrived%20at%20an%20arrangement%20under%20which%20Julfikar%20sent%20patients%20who%20needed%20operation%20for%20kidney%2C%20gall%20bladder%20stones%20to%20the%20clinic.%20He%20also%20sent%20pregnant%20women%20for%20delivery%20and%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Neeraj%20Aggarwal%20agreed%20to%20pay%20him%2035%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20amount%20billed%20by%20each%20patient.%20The%20money%20was%20transferred%20through%20UPI%2C%20sources%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrangement%20has%20been%20running%20for%20around%20six%20years%2C%20sources%20said.%20The%20last%20patient%20he%20sent%20was%20Asgar%20Ali%2C%20who%20died%20during%20treatment.%20Asghar%20Ali%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20clinic%20in%202022%20for%20gallbladder%20surgery%2C%20which%20was%20allegedly%20conducted%20by%20Pooja%20Agarwal%20and%20Mahendra%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJulfikar%20used%20to%20send%20around%2040%20to%2050%20patients%20per%20month%2Fyear%20to%20the%20Agarwal%20Medical%20Centre.%20With%20Dr%20Neeraj%20Aggarwal%20charging%20Rs%2015%2C000%20to%2020%2C000%20for%20delivery%2C%20stone%20operation%20and%20Rs%205000%20to%20Rs%206000%20for%20abortions%2C%20Julfikar%20earned%20a%20substantial%20amount%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20since%202016%2C%20there%20have%20been%20at%20least%20nine%20complaints%20against%20Dr%20Agarwal%2C%20Pooja%20and%20the%20Agarwal%20Medical%20Centre.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20seven%20cases%2C%20patients%20died%20due%20to%20medical%20negligence%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20has%20reported%2C%20quoting%20police%20sources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700399040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F8iaaicq8_greater-kailash-fake-doctors-_625x300_16_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-delhi-medical-racket-that-cost-lives-co