%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20September%202021%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nugmyanmar.org%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3ENational%20Unity%20Government%20(NUG)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20shadow%20government%20in%20exile%2C%20has%20authorised%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D563426214705678%5C%22%3Edefensive%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20state%20military%2C%20pushing%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20militias%20targeting%20the%20junta%20and%20its%20economic%20base.%20NUG%20militias%20have%20increasingly%20coordinated%20with%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20dozens%20of%20ethnic%20armed%20groups%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20already%20been%20fighting%20the%20Tatmadaw%20(the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20military)%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20every%20time%20government%20troops%20leave%20their%20barracks%20they%20face%20potential%20attack%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20increasingly%20lean%20on%20air%20power%2C%20but%20further%20limiting%20their%20ability%20to%20maintain%20effective%20control%20on%20the%20ground.%20Economic%20and%20territorial%20losses%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmyanmar.iiss.org%2F%5C%22%3Esteadily%20accumulated%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20important%20because%20the%20Tatmadaw%E2%80%99s%20legitimacy%20depends%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20hold%20the%20country%20together.%20The%20controversial%202008%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.burmalibrary.org%2Fdocs5%2FMyanmar_Constitution-2008-en.pdf%5C%22%3Emilitary-drafted%20constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%20refers%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnon-disintegration%E2%80%9D%20of%20Myanmar%20a%20dozen%20times%2C%20including%20as%20a%20duty%20of%20the%20defence%20forces.%20This%20was%20a%20key%20justification%20for%20the%201962%20military%20coup%20that%20ushered%20in%20five%20decades%20of%20military%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20immediate%20post-independence%20period%20(1948-1962)%2C%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20civilian%20government%20struggled%20to%20maintain%20territorial%20control%2C%20at%20times%20controlling%20little%20more%20than%20major%20urban%20centres.%20The%20situation%20is%20similar%20now%2C%20except%20that%20today%20it%20is%20the%20Tatmadaw%20that%20is%20unable%20to%20maintain%20control%20beyond%20urban%20centres%20and%20military%20barracks.%20This%20will%20hit%20junta%20morale%20badly%20and%20inspire%20further%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junta%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fwar-against-the-junta%2Fnine-towns-occupied-by-myanmar-military-for-decades-lost-to-resistance-in-days.html%5C%22%3Erecent%20reversal%20in%20Shan%20State%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20most%20significant%20territorial%20loss%2C%20came%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20three%20ethnic-based%20armed%20groups%2C%20the%20Arakan%20Army%2C%20Myanmar%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20Army%2C%20and%20the%20Ta%E2%80%99ang%20National%20Liberation%20Army.%20These%20three%20groups%20now%20coordinate%20their%20activities%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fenglish%2Fcommentaries%2Fmyanmar-operation-1027-11102023122533.html%5C%22%3EBrotherhood%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fwar-against-the-junta%2Fmyanmar-military-chiefs-gather-for-emergency-meeting.html%5C%22%3Einflicted%20heavy%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20junta%20forces%20in%20early%20November%2C%20overrunning%20dozens%20of%20military%20posts%20and%20killing%20the%20commander%20of%20the%2099th%20Light%20Infantry%20Division%2C%20a%20unit%20known%20internationally%20for%20its%20genocidal%20campaign%20against%20the%20Rohingya%20community.%20The%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20also%20captured%20the%20main%20overland%20route%20from%20Mandalay%20to%20China%2C%20a%20key%20economic%20corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrotherhood%20Alliance%20members%20are%20themselves%20territorially%20ambitious%2C%20but%20rely%20on%20China%20for%20arms%20so%20it%20is%20unlikely%20an%20operation%20in%20China%E2%80%99s%20hinterland%20could%20have%20occurred%20without%20China%E2%80%99s%20acquiescence.%20Allowing%20this%20operation%20to%20go%20ahead%20is%20a%20strong%20statement%20by%20a%20Chinese%20government%20frustrated%20with%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20inaction%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bangkokpost.com%2Fthailand%2Fgeneral%2F2618314%2Fchina-tells-myanmar-to-root-out-scam-gangs%5C%22%3Eonline%20scam%20centres%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Shan%20State%20where%20thousands%20of%20trafficked%20Chinese%20and%20other%20foreigners%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20work%20in%20slave-like%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20ambiguity%20is%20unsurprising.%20China%20was%20far%20from%20enthusiastic%20about%20the%202021%20coup.%20China%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20to%20Myanmar%2C%20Chen%20Hai%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fburma%2Fambassador-tries-calm-anti-china-feeling-myanmar-following-coup.html%5C%22%3Etold%20journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%20a%20coup%20was%2C%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20not%20what%20China%20wants%20to%20see%E2%80%9D.%20While%20traditionally%20a%20key%20international%20ally%20of%20the%20junta%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20had%20a%20very%20close%20relationship%20with%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20ousted%20de%20facto%20leader%2C%20Aung%20San%20Suu%20Kyi%2C%20and%20maintains%20close%20ties%20with%20many%20of%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20ethnic%20armed%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20strategic%20reversals%2C%20nationwide%20territorial%20losses%20and%20economic%20decline%20mean%20momentum%20has%20strongly%20shifted%20away%20from%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20junta.%20China%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20may%20have%20read%20the%20situation%20better%20than%20most%2C%20recognising%20the%20junta%20may%20now%20be%20in%20a%20death%20spiral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20been%20less%20shrewd.%20Russia%20has%20displaced%20China%20as%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2F05%2Fun-expert-exposes-1-billion-death-trade-myanmar-military%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20arms%20supplier%3C%2Fa%3E%20accounting%20for%20US%24406%20million%20(%C2%A3326.5%20million)%20of%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20arms%20imports%20since%20the%20coup%20and%20crucially%20providing%20aviation%20fuel%20in%20exchange%20for%20funds%2C%20access%20to%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20port%20facilities%2C%20and%20regional%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoup%20leader%20Min%20Aung%20Hlaing%20recently%20welcomed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-myanmar-navy-andaman-sea-1d0f0c692a4583a0c449e6c8cc3b620b%5C%22%3ERussia%E2%80%99s%20navy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20joint%20manoeuvres%2C%20describing%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20glowing%20terms%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cleader%20of%20the%20world%20who%20is%20creating%20stability%20on%20the%20international%20arena%E2%80%9D.%20For%20Putin%2C%20this%20may%20soon%20be%20embarrassingly%20unwelcome%20praise.%20By%20linking%20itself%20so%20closely%20with%20a%20declining%20junta%2C%20Russia%20guarantees%20its%20Myanmar%20influence%20and%20regional%20relevance%20will%20not%20outlast%20military%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPost-junta%20planning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NUG%20idealises%20a%20post-junta%20Myanmar%20unified%20under%20its%20leadership%20with%20Aung%20San%20Suu%20Kyi%20returned%20to%20power.%20But%20for%20many%20ethnic%20armed%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20who%20will%20feel%20they%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20NUG%2C%20inflicted%20the%20strongest%20blows%20on%20the%20junta%20and%20now%20control%20significant%20territory%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20not%20likely%20their%20preferred%20outcome.%20They%20will%20seek%20guarantees%20about%20key%20demands%20around%20federalism%20and%20minority%20rights%20that%20were%20not%20satisfactorily%20addressed%20when%20Aung%20San%20was%20last%20in%20power.%3C%2