dy%20conducted%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Utah%20to%20elucidate%20her%20choice%20to%20withdraw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20a%20study%2C%20a%20male%20blow%20has%20163%25%20more%20impact%20than%20a%20woman's%2C%20even%20adjusted%20for%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Bissonnette%20said.%20She%20argued%20that%20biologically%20female%20athletes%20should%20not%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20%26quot%3Bphysical%20and%20psychological%20risks%26quot%3B%20brought%20on%20by%20an%20opponent's%20decisions%20regarding%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bidentity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ms%20Walmsley%20was%20not%20happy%20about%20Ms%20Bissonnette's%20decision%20to%20withdraw.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRather%20than%20turning%20to%20me%2C%20my%20coach%20or%20the%20Quebec%20Olympic%20Boxing%20Federation%20for%20more%20information%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20turn%20directly%20to%20the%20media%20to%20out%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Walmsley%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThis%20kind%20of%20behaviour%20puts%20athletes%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20excluded%20or%20receiving%20personal%20attacks%20based%20on%20hearsay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Walmsley%20suggested%20that%20Bissonnette's%20allegations%20might%20be%20employed%20to%20undermine%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20transgender%20female%20athletes%20and%20support%20specific%20regulations.%20The%20boxer%20advocates%20for%20mutual%20trust%20among%20athletes%20regarding%20gender%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReportedly%2C%20Ms%20Bissonnette%20asserts%20that%20the%20Australian%20athlete%20would%20have%20been%20ineligible%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20women's%20category%20in%20her%20home%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Walmsley)%20would%20have%20boxed%20as%20a%20man%20in%20Australia%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Bissonnette%20alleged.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Quebec%2C%20on%20his%20%5Bsic%5D%20file%2C%20it%20is%20mentioned%20that%20he%20%5Bsic%5D%20had%20zero%20fights%20as%20a%20woman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReportedly%2C%20Ms%20Bissonnette%20holds%20the%20view%20that%20sports%20categories%20should%20be%20restricted%20to%20separate%20divisions%20for%20biological%20males%20and%20females.%20This%20perspective%20appears%20to%20resonate%20with%20government%20leaders%20across%20the%20nation%2C%20as%20nine%20Republican%20governors%20urged%20the%20NCAA%20to%20reassess%20its%20policy%20on%20the%20inclusion%20of%20transgender%20athletes%20in%20a%20letter%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NCAA%20has%20the%20chance%20to%20guarantee%20an%20environment%20where%20female%20college%20athletes%20can%20thrive%20without%20the%20concern%20of%20inequities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governors%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20trust%20that%20you%20also%20want%20to%20guarantee%20just%20such%20an%20environment.%20But%20this%20policy%20allows%20the%20NCAA%20to%20avoid%20responsibility%20for%20ensuring%20the%20fairness%20of%20collegiate%20sports%20-therefore%20it%20must%20be%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700396580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F04t2sn1_katia-bissonnette_625x300_19_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanadian-boxer-withdraws-from-championship-after-discovering-opponent-is-transgender-4587303%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Walmsley%20secured%20victory%20by%20default%20as%20officials%20were%20unable%20to%20locate%20another%20boxer%20in%20the%20corresponding%20weight%20class.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanadian-boxer-withdraws-from-championship-after-discovering-opponent-is-transgender-4587303%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanadian-boxer-withdraws-from-championship-after-discovering-opponent-is-transgender-4587303%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampU