0in%20LA%2C%20so%20she%20ranked%20that%20first.%20She%20also%20had%20dreams%20of%20living%20in%20New%20York%2C%20so%20she%20put%20that%20as%20her%20second%20choice.%20Below%20that%20were%20cities%20like%20Fort%20Lauderdale%2C%20Florida%3B%20Boston%2C%20Massachusetts%3B%20and%20Orlando%2C%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon%20said%20at%20the%20time%20she%20knew%20getting%20placed%20in%20LA%20was%20unlikely.%20For%20JetBlue%2C%20LA%20was%20a%20senior%20base.%20This%20means%20the%20airport%20had%20appealing%20flights%20and%20flight%20times%2C%20and%20therefore%20senior%20flight%20attendants%20sought%20that%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22London%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20at%20JetBlue.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65562ad422cf74a57398577d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELondon%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20at%20JetBlue.%3Cp%3E%40londonkaizen%2FTikTok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJFK%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20what's%20considered%20a%20junior%20base.%20It%20had%20worse%20flights%20and%20flight%20times.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20in%20an%20expensive%20city%2C%20so%20fewer%20flight%20attendants%20with%20seniority%20want%20to%20work%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon%20said%20she%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20good%20chance%20she%20was%20moving%20to%20New%20York.%20But%20when%20she%20opened%20the%20email%20revealing%20her%20base%2C%20she%20had%20been%20assigned%20to%20Boston%20%E2%80%94%20her%20fourth%20choice.%20In%20fact%2C%20her%20entire%20class%20of%20trainees%20was%20headed%20to%20Boston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoston%20is%20completely%20different%20from%20LA%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20never%20spent%20any%20time%20there%20and%20then%20thinking%20about%20spending%20all%20the%20time%20there%2C%20my%20emotions%20weren't%20the%20happiest%2C%20naturally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon%20had%20a%20choice%20to%20make%20since%20the%20airline%20wasn't%20going%20to%20force%20her%20to%20move.%20She%20could%20still%20live%20in%20LA%20while%20commuting%20to%20Boston%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlight%20attendants%20aren't%20required%20to%20live%20in%20their%20base%20cities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20London%20said%20that%20it's%20typically%20encouraged%20to%20live%20in%20your%20base%20city%20as%20a%20new%20flight%20attendant%2C%20few%20airlines%20require%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20flight%20attendants%20can%20commute%20to%20their%20base%20cities%20and%20spend%20their%20working%20nights%20in%20hotels%2C%20temporary%20apartments%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fflight-attendant-crash-pad-where-airline-employees-sleep-photos-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecrash%20pads%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20affordable%20dorm-like%20accommodations%20specifically%20for%20airline%20crews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20basically%20decide%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20commute%20or%20move%20completely%20across%20the%20country%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20London%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20commuting%20via%20a%20five-and-a-half-hour%20flight%20didn't%20make%20sense.%20So%20London%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20flight%20attendants%20in%20her%20training%20class%2C%20moved%20into%20a%20Boston%20apartment%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20wasn't%20initially%20thrilled%20with%20the%20situation%2C%20London%20said%20%26quot%3Bit%20actually%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20best%20thing%20that%20happened%20to%20me%20in%20the%20end.%26quot%3B%20She%20made%20new%20friends%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20a%20brand-new%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcIntyre%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20decided%20to%20commute%20after%20her%20base%20reveal%20at%20the%20regional%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20been%20assigned%20to%20Dayton%2C%20Ohio.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20living%20in%20a%20completely%20different%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20didn't%20want%20to%20pack%20up%20her%20entire%20life%20to%20live%20in%20Dayton%2C%20so%20she%20landed%20on%20commuting.%20Every%20week%2C%20she'd%20fly%20into%20Dayton%20and%20spend%20her%20nights%20in%20a%20crashpad%2C%20which%20she%20said%20she%20paid%20about%20%24300%20a%20month%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20flight%20attendants%20can%20immediately%20request%20a%20transfer%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they'll%20get%20one%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flight%20attendants%20gather%20their%20belongings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6556539d22cf74a57398958e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENot%20everyone%20ends%20up%20at%20their%20top%20city.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Zalubowski%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20flight%20attendant%20isn't%20happy%20with%20their%20base%20assignment%2C%20many%20airlines%20will%20allow%20them%20to%20request%20a%20transfer%2C%20McIntyre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20case%20for%20every%20airline%2C%20Parker%20said.%20Her%20airline%20requires%20flight%20attendants%20to%20complete%20a%20six-month%20probationary%20period%20before%20they%20can%20submit%20a%20bid%20to%20transfer%20to%20a%20new%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20six%20months%2C%20they%20can%20apply%20to%20move%20around%20as%20much%20as%20they'd%20like%20throughout%20their%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon%20remembers%20the%20storm%20of%20emotions%20her%20training%20class%20experienced%20as%20they%20discovered%20they%20were%20all%20going%20to%20Boston.%20Some%20were%20thrilled%20they'd%20be%20in%20the%20same%20city%20with%20their%20newfound%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20were%20heartbroken%20to%20realize%20that%20their%20lives%20were%20about%20to%20drastically%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20a%20state%20in%20my%20life%20where%20I%20wanted%20some%20change%20versus%20some%20of%20my%20classmates%20who%20had%20family%20and%20children%20and%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20people%20who%20weren't%20happy%20with%20their%20base%20assignment%20could%20request%20a%20transfer%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransfers%20work%20based%20on%20which%20cities%20need%20flight%20attendants.%20They%20can%20take%20weeks%20and%20months%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20flight%20attendants%20said.%20And%20if%20a%20flight%20attendant%20agrees%20to%20a%20transfer%2C%20they're%20required%20to%20be%20in%20their%20new%20city%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20months%2C%20London%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20build%20more%20seniority%20with%20the%20company%2C%20London%20said%20moving%20and%20switching%20bases%20is%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20cities%2C%20like%20Miami%20and%20Houston%2C%20are%20bases%20for%20more%20senior%20employees%20where%20new%20hires%20shouldn't%20expect%20to%20be%20placed%20right%20away.%20But%2C%20places%20like%20New%20York%20City%20and%20Austin%20are%20more%20realistic%20choices%20for%20junior%20flight%20attendants%2C%20Parker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20London%2C%20who%20has%20now%20worked%20at%20JetBlue%20for%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20Boston%20has%20remained%20the%20unexpected%20place%20she%20calls%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendants-explain-how-base-city-chosen-viral-videos-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700396041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655668c34ca513d8242ad38a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendants-explain-how-base-city-chosen-viral-videos-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Viral%20videos%20show%20flight%20attendants%20rejoicing%20or%20looking%20miserable%20about%20their%20new%20hom