dent%20snagged%20an%20internship%20at%20a%20major%20consulting%20firm%20last%20summer%20and%20accepted%20an%20offer%20to%20return%20full-time%20after%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20job%20win%20comes%20as%20the%20field%20of%20consulting%20isn't%20as%20red-hot%20as%20it%20was%20in%202021%20and%202022%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20slowdown%2C%20MBA%20students%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia%20Darden%20School%20of%20Business%20aren't%20all%20stampeding%20toward%20consulting%20as%20many%20had%20for%20a%20time%2C%20Jeff%20McNish%2C%20an%20assistant%20dean%20at%20the%20Darden%20Career%20Center%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20driving%20our%20students%20to%20think%20broader%20about%20their%20post-MBA%20career%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20all%20doom%20and%20gloom.%20I%20just%20think%20it's%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeading%20into%20this%20year%2C%20some%20B-school%20students%20might%20have%20expected%20a%20slew%20of%20offers%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20they%20saw%20MBA%20graduates%20from%20recent%20years%20enjoy.%20But%20now%20a%20range%20of%20companies%20are%20being%20more%20deliberate%20about%20how%20quickly%20they're%20hiring%20MBAs%2C%20administrators%20told%20BI.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20BI%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firm-new-hires-consultants-mba-get-paid-do-nothing-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Econsultancies%20were%20pushing%20back%20start%20dates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20or%20telling%20those%20with%20new%20MBA%20credentials%20appended%20to%20their%20LinkedIn%20profiles%20that%20they%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenz-startup-founder-recruiting-consulting-bcg-bain-mckinsey-class-2023-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ego%20do%20something%20else%20for%20a%20while%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%202023%20seems%20like%20a%20rough%20job%20market.%20However%2C%20it's%20actually%20close%20to%20a%20normal%20market%20for%20MBA%20grads%2C%20industry%20and%20career%20experts%20told%20BI.%20Though%20there%20are%20fewer%20offers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20might%20take%20longer%20to%20materialize%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20the%20letters%20are%20still%20coming%2C%20career%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20that's%20leaving%20some%20MBA%20students%20uneasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20understanding%20is%20the%20environment%20today%20looks%20a%20lot%20more%20like%20the%20environment%20of%20'18%20and%20'19%20than%20it%20does%20to%20'21%2C%20'22.%20But%20that's%20not%20a%20bad%20environment%2C%20per%20se.%20It's%20just%20not%20what%20folks%20were%20accustomed%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20student%20said.%20BI%20granted%20him%20anonymity%20because%20he's%20not%20authorized%20by%20his%20future%20employer%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoing%20back%20in%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECareer-services%20administrators%20echoed%20the%20return-to-normal%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20in%20any%20stretch%20a%20recession%20or%20MBAs%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20in%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20McNish%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20maybe%20irrational%20exuberance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHiring%20just%20went%20off%20the%20charts%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20since%20come%20back%20down.%20Even%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20one%20of%20the%20MBB%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0McKinsey%2C%20Bain%2C%20and%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20%E2%80%94%20firms%20so%20coveted%20by%20business%20students%2C%20earlier%20this%20year%20offered%20some%20new%20MBAs%20payouts%20to%20go%20work%20for%20a%20nonprofit%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbain-consulting-offering-new-hires-delay-start-yoga-safari-report-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%2420%2C000%20to%20become%20yoga%20instructors%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20pushed-back%20start%20dates%20in%20April%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephanie%20O'Connor%2C%20associate%20dean%20for%20career%20services%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20Booth%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20told%20BI%20tech%20companies%20in%20recent%20years%20had%20been%20more%20comfortable%20making%20offers%20to%20students%20shortly%20after%20a%20summer%20internship%20ended.%20While%20that's%20fairly%20common%20in%20fields%20like%20consulting%20and%20investment%20banking%2C%20she%20noted%2C%20speedy%20offers%20aren't%20always%20the%20norm%20for%20tech%20and%20some%20other%20corporate%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20compared%20with%20prior%20years%2C%20she's%20seeing%20a%20%26quot%3Bslightly%20lower%26quot%3B%20percentage%20of%20students%20getting%20offers%20to%20return%20full-time%20to%20a%20company.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20almost%20like%20more%20of%20a%20normal%20return%20rate%2C%20but%20because%20we've%20had%20such%20high%20yields%20and%20high%20return-offer%20rates%20for%20internship%20classes%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20shock%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20stabilizing%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20O'Connor%20thinks%20the%20environment%20could%20be%20stabilizing%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20feel%20almost%20like%20we're%20approaching%20a%20normal%20year%20as%20opposed%20to%20hitting%20a%20lot%20of%20bumps%20in%20the%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20This%20comes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-unemployment-rate-recession-outlook-labor-market-wages-federal-reserve-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edemand%20for%20workers%20remains%20tight%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20many%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Ivy%20League%20student%2C%20watching%20artificial%20intelligence%20exp