while%20playing%20in%20the%20front%20yard%20of%20a%20home%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F11%2F17%2Fnews%2Fpuppy-rescued-after-spending-eight-hours-inside-of-sewer%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20New%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20San%20Antonio%20Fire%20Department%20pulled%20two%20puppies%20to%20safety%2C%20however%2C%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20catch%20the%20third%20one%2C%20who%20had%20crawled%20deeper%20into%20the%20sewer%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extensive%20rescue%20operation%20began%20when%20the%20department%20called%20the%20San%20Antonio%20Water%20System%20for%20help.%20Using%20a%20tiny%20camera%2C%20the%20personnel%20found%20the%20dog%20inside%20the%20sewer%20and%20gently%20redirected%20it%20200%20feet%20to%20a%20sewage%20opening%20found%20across%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20eight%20hours%2C%20the%20pooch%2C%20which%20was%20named%20Pipa%20by%20the%20responders%20was%20pulled%20out%20and%20rescued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20giving%20Pipa%20back%20to%20its%20owners%2C%20San%20Antonio%20Animal%20Care%20Services%20brought%20her%20to%20a%20nearby%20veterinarian%20for%20an%20examination.%20Although%20the%20officials%20stated%20that%20there%20aren't%20many%20instances%20of%20dogs%20falling%20into%20private%20sewer%20systems%2C%20they%20nevertheless%20advised%20locals%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20clean-out%20valves%20are%20correctly%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20a%20four-month-old%20Labrador%20dog%20was%20rescued%20by%20British%20firefighters%20after%20getting%20its%20head%20caught%20in%20a%20wall.%20The%20name%20of%20the%20adventurous%20puppy%20is%20Teale%2C%20who%20got%20stuck%20in%20an%20extractor%20vent%20for%20a%20tumble%20dryer%20in%20Longtown%2C%20Carlisle.%20Firefighters%20were%20able%20to%20rescue%20the%20four-month-old%20puppy%20after%20the%20dog's%20owners%20summoned%20emergency%20services%20to%20free%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20details%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20Carlisle%20East%20Fire%20Station%20stated%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%2016.15%20p.m.%2C%20Carlisle%20East%20was%20mobilised%20to%20a%20property%20in%20Longtown%20to%20reports%20of%20a%20young%20dog%20with%20its%20head%20stuck%20in%20a%20wall.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIn%20attendance%2C%20the%20crew%20were%20greeted%20by%20a%20mischievous%204-month-old%20labrador%20puppy%20called%20Teale%2C%20who%20had%20found%20herself%20in%20a%20predicament%20by%20getting%20her%20head%20stuck%20in%20an%20extractor%20vent%20for%20a%20tumble%20dryer%20and%20was%20feeling%20very%20sorry%20for%20herself.%20Fortunately%2C%20crews%20managed%20to%20remove%20Teale%20with%20minimal%20fuss%20using%20small%20tools%2C%20and%20she%20was%20no%20worse%20for%20wear%20for%20her%20ordeal.%20She%20was%20very%20appreciative%2C%20and%20she%20rewarded%20the%20crew%20with%20lots%20of%20cuddles%20and%20licks!%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700394000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgfti8tf_aa_625x300_19_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpuppy-rescued-after-being-trapped-for-8-hours-in-us-sewer-4587217%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20nearly%20eight%20hours%2C%20the%20pooch%2C%20which%20was%20named%20Pipa%20by%20the%20responders%20was%20pulled%20out%20and%20rescued.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpuppy-rescued-after-being-trapped-for-8-hours-in-us-sewer-4587217%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpuppy-rescued-after-being-trapped-for-8-hours-in-us-sewer-4587217%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpuppy-rescued-after-being-trapped-for-8-hours-in-us-sewer-4587217%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20may%20take%20part%20in%20India-led%20G