is%20available.%20There%20is%20a%204-inch%20pipe%2C%20which%20was%20used%20for%20compression.%20Through%20that%2C%20we%20are%20sending%20food%20from%20day%201%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%2C%20in%20a%20video%20brief%20update%20on%20the%20Uttarkashi%20tunnel%20collapse%20rescue%20operation%2C%20further%20said%20there%20is%20water%20and%20electricity%20in%20two%20km%20portion%20inside%20the%20tunnel%2C%20which%20is%20the%20finished%20part%20of%20the%204.531-kilometre%20two%20lane%20bi-directional%20tunnel%20at%20Silkyara%20in%20Uttarkashi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20sending%20multivitamins%2C%20antidepressants%20and%20dry%20fruits%20to%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20trapped%20inside%20the%20under-construction%20tunnel%20at%20Silkyara%20in%20Uttarkashi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Silkyara%20tunnel%2C%20about%2030%20km%20from%20the%20district%20headquarters%20of%20Uttarkashi%20and%20a%20seven-hour%20drive%20from%20the%20Uttarakhand%20capital%20Dehradun%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20all-weather%20road%20project%20of%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%20is%20being%20constructed%20under%20the%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20(NHIDCL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnel%20collapsed%20around%205.30%20am%20last%20Sunday.%20The%20rescue%20operation%20was%20suspended%20on%20Friday%20afternoon%20when%20a%20US-made%20auger%20machine%20deployed%20to%20drill%20and%20push%20in%20pipes%20through%20the%20rubble%20to%20prepare%20an%20escape%20passage%20for%20the%20workers%20developed%20a%20snag%20that%20exacerbated%20the%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20drilling%20was%20halted%2C%20the%20auger%20machine%20had%20drilled%20up%20to%2024%20metres%20through%20the%20rubble%2C%20spread%20over%20a%2060-metre%20area%20inside%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20also%20held%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20on%20Saturday%20where%20five%20options%20to%20rescue%20the%20workers%20were%20discussed%20with%20different%20agencies%20assigned%20with%20specific%20alternatives%20to%20work%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENHIDCL%20MD%20Mahmood%20Ahmed%20has%20been%20made%20in%20charge%20of%20coordination%20with%20all%20the%20central%20agencies%20and%20has%20been%20stationed%20in%20Silkyara.%20%C2%A0ONGC%2C%20RVNL%2C%20Satluj%20Jal%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Ltd%2C%20BRO%20and%20state%20PWD%2C%20besides%20NHIDCL%2C%20will%20be%20the%20agencies%20carrying%20out%20different%20responsibilities%20to%20establish%20early%20access%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20operations%20stalled%20around%202.45%20pm%20on%20Friday.%20During%20the%20positioning%20of%20a%20fifth%20pipe%2C%20a%20big%20cracking%20sound%20was%20heard%20in%20the%20tunnel%2C%20after%20which%20rescue%20operation%20was%20suspended%20immediately%2C%20a%20statement%20from%20NHIDCL%20--%20tasked%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20tunnel%20--%20said%20on%20Friday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sound%20created%20panic%20among%20the%20rescue%20team.%20An%20expert%20involved%20with%20the%20project%20warned%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20further%20collapse%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20pipe-pushing%20activity%20was%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700393040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ff801h1r_uttarakhand-tunnel_625x300_19_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fantidepressants-dry-fruit-for-41-workers-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-4587178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20is%20sending%20multivitamins%2C%20antidepressants%20and%20dry%20fruits%20to%2041%20workers%20trapped%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20d