She%20recalled%20her%20first%20teaching%20job%20at%20an%20alternative%20education%20school%20and%20being%20able%20to%20help%20students%20beyond%20the%20classroom.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bunderstood%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20be%20heard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20felt%20this%20sense%20of%20connection%20with%20these%20kids%20that%20were%20unable%20to%20connect%20with%20society%20was%20really%2C%20really%20fulfilling%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonna%20described%20herself%20as%20a%20strict%20substitute%20teacher%20but%20believes%20school%20should%20be%20a%20joyful%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20show%20them%20a%20lesson%20plan%20and%20I%20go%2C%20my%20job%20is%20to%20get%20through%20this%20with%20you%20guys%20today%2C%20so%20we're%20going%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Donna%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20kids%20have%20respect%20for%20me.%20It%20takes%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20work%20and%20classroom%20management%20skills%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%2C%20because%20some%20subs%20don't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20new%20subs%20come%20in%20with%20their%20novels%2C%20and%20they're%20just%20going%20to%20sit%20there%20and%20read%20during%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Donna%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'm%20sad%20for%20that%20because%20it's%20a%20lost%20day%20of%20learning.%20So%20I%20take%20my%20job%20as%20a%20sub%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFinding%20her%20freedom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20few%20career%20changes%20in%20a%20few%20different%20fields%2C%20Donna%20has%20learned%20that%20it%20is%20really%20up%20to%20her%20how%20much%20she%20wants%20to%20get%20paid%20at%20a%20job%20and%20where%20she%20wants%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20most%20of%20my%20career%2C%20I%20gave%20that%20to%20somebody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Donna%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20get%20to%20decide%20when%20you%20work%2C%20what%20to%20do%20and%20all%20that.%20I'm%20like%2C%20wait%20a%20minute.%20I%20can%20take%20that%20power%20back.%20And%20this%20teaching%20experience%20has%20made%20me%20realize%20that.%20It's%20very%20freeing.%20It's%20very%20liberating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20has%20done%20some%20occasional%20work%20in%20the%20senior%20care%20industry%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonna%20said%20she%20doesn't%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennials-baby-boomers-jobs-employment-changes-glassdoor-report-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efull-time%20position%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bwent%20to%20college%20and%20grad%20school%20later%20in%20life.%26quot%3B%20Before%20college%20she%20worked%20in%20high%20tech%2C%20recalling%20that%20this%20pay%20was%20pretty%20low%20back%20in%20the%20'80s.%20She%20said%20she%20then%20worked%20in%20the%20senior%20care%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20did%20sales%20in%20the%20senior%20care%20industry%20before%20moving%20into%20operational%20leadership%20work%20in%20the%20industry.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20frequently%20traveling%20during%20leadership%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20making%20six%20figures%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20that%20it%20was%20kind%20of%20soul%20sucking%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Donna%20said%2C%20noting%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20%26quot%3Bemotional%20issues%26quot%3B%20involved%2C%20such%20as%20people%20who%20have%20lost%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20daily%20living%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonna%20said%20she%20left%20the%20industry%20and%20did%20a%20teaching%20program%20where%20she%20was%20teaching%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20learning%20how%20to%20become%20a%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20did%20return%20to%20the%20senior%20care%20industry%20and%20held%20a%20job%20in%20senior%20care%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20Being%20in%20leadership%20during%20this%20time%20she%20sa