E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20state%2C%20a%20viable%20solution%20to%20the%20conflict%20can%20only%20be%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20We%20consider%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20India%20is%20the%20only%20hope%20for%20bringing%20peace%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20who%20has%20not%20visited%20strife%20torn%20Manipur%20in%20the%20six%20months%20of%20the%20conflict%20has%20faced%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties%20for%20not%20speaking%20on%20the%20issue.%20On%20August%2010%2C%20the%20second%20last%20day%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebroke%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20parliament%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20while%20replying%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20moved%20against%20his%20government.%20However%2C%20in%20his%20speech%20that%20lasted%20around%202%20hours%2020%20mins%2C%20Modi%20spoke%20about%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-as-violence-rages-on-mlas-divided-over-whether-or-not-to-hold-special-assembly-session%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20violence%20hit-state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-gives-mizoram-election-rally-a-miss-is-manipur-mayhem-the-reason%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egave%20a%20miss%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20campaigning%20in%20election%20bound%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%20%E2%80%93%20the%20one%20state%20election%20where%20the%20prime%20minister%20did%20not%20go%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%