times.com%2Fphoto%2F105293412.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAt%20the%201994%20Miss%20Universe%20beauty%20pageant%2C%20Sushmita%20Sen%20made%20a%20bold%20and%20budget-friendly%20statement%20by%20eschewing%20a%20high-end%20designer%20gown.%20Financial%20constraints%20led%20her%20to%20opt%20for%20a%20dress%20crafted%20by%20a%20local%20tailor%20in%20Delhi%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20lavish%20ensembles%20typically%20associated%20with%20such%20competitions.%20In%20a%20resourceful%20touch%2C%20even%20the%20elegant%20gloves%20she%20donned%20during%20the%20final%20round%20were%20ingeniously%20fashioned%20from%20socks%2C%20skillfully%20trimmed%20by%20her%20mother.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Ode%20to%20the%20101-Year%20Old%20Freedom%20Fighter%20and%20Communist%20N.%20Sankaraiah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19134216%2FN.Sankaraiah_CPIM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EN.%20Sankaraiah%20died%20in%20Chennai%20on%20November%2015%2C%202023%20and%20was%20cremated%20with%20state%20honours.%20A%20younger%20associate%20remembers%20his%20warmth%20and%20fiery%20radicalism%20that%20came%20through%20well%20unto%20his%20last%20days.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENovember%207%20is%20a%20day%20of%20uprising%20for%20Communists%20across%20the%20world.%20On%20this%20day%2C%20a%20social%20revolution%20was%20ushered%20in%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Lenin.%20This%20year%2C%20on%20that%20day%2C%20the%20renovated%20state%20committee%20office%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20CPI(M)%20was%20declared%20open.%20Along%20with%20it%2C%20the%20event%20to%20unveil%20the%20statue%20of%20P.%20Ramamurthy%2C%20a%20veteran%20Communist%20leader%20and%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20valedictory%20event%20on%20that%20day%2C%20B.%20Ramamurthy%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20and%20acclaimed%20lawyer%20Vaigai%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20very%20slogan%20%3Cem%3EInquilab%20Zindabad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(long%20live%20the%20revolution)%20terrorises%20this%20government.%20We%20need%20to%20keep%20raising%20this%20slogan%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20she%20ended%20her%20speech%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESankaraiah%2C%20who%20had%20sent%20an%20audio%20message%20felicitating%20the%20event%2C%20had%20also%20ended%20his%20note%20with%20Inquilab%20Zindabad.%20The%20majesty%20in%20his%20voice%20was%20almost%20intact.%20Everyone%20at%20the%20event%20including%20Vaigai%20on%20the%20dais%20were%20moved%20to%20tears%20on%20hearing%20the%20voice.%20Within%20a%20week%2C%20comrade%20Sankaraiah%20left%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16092418%2F04a-2013-JULY-20-2-PS-Sankariah-Nine_decad.max-1400x1120-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16092418%2F04a-2013-JULY-20-2-PS-Sankariah-Nine_decad.max-1400x1120-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16092418%2F04a-2013-JULY-20-2-PS-Sankariah-Nine_decad.max-1400x1120-1-300x218.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16092418%2F04a-2013-JULY-20-2-PS-Sankariah-Nine_decad.max-1400x1120-1-1024x745.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684995%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22873%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESankaraiah%20in%20his%20party%20office%20library%20in%202013%20%E2%80%93%20he%20had%20just%20inaugurated%20it.%20Photo%3A%20S.%20Gavaskar%2F%20People%E2%80%99s%20Archive%20of%20Rural%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComrade%20Sankaraiah%20appeared%20as%20a%20formidable%20leader%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20face%20of%20British%20imperialism.%20Because%20of%20which%20he%20had%20faced%20numerous%20prison%20sentences.%20By%20the%20time%20he%20turned%2040%2C%20he%20had%20already%20served%20eight%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20three%20years%20underground.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20was%20in%20full%20swing%2C%20Sankariah%2C%20a%20student%20of%20The%20American%20College%20in%20Madurai%2C%20mobilised%20the%20students%20in%20the%20college%20and%20got%20them%20involved%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20When%20Netaji%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Bose%20visited%20Chennai%2C%20it%20was%20Sankaraiah%20who%20brought%20him%20to%20Madurai%20and%20instilled%20the%20spirit%20of%20freedom%20struggle%20among%20the%20students%20through%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Sankariah%20who%20formed%20and%20guided%20a%20student%20organisation%20to%20mobilise%20the%20students%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20towards%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20He%20started%20with%20Madurai%20and%20organised%20students%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20different%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201964%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20or%20CPI(M)%20was%20formed%20after%20an%20ideological%20split%20within%20the%20Communist%20movement.%20Comrade%20Sankaraiah%20was%20among%20the%2032%20national%20executive%20members%20who%20formed%20the%20CPI(M).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CVanakkam%2C%20comrade%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20many%20special%20traits%20of%20comrade%20Sankaraiah%E2%80%99s%20character%20in%20my%20own%20student%20days.%20When%20the%20police%20resorted%20to%20lathi-charge%20after%20a%20protest%20at%20the%20Chrompet%20government%20school%20where%20I%20was%20studying%2C%20I%20ran%20to%20Sankaraiah%E2%80%99s%20house%20seeking%20refuge.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20ignorant%20of%20his%20history%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20was%20a%20veteran%20communist%20leader%20and%20freedom%20fighter.%20%E2%80%9CThatha%2C%20thaatha%20(Grandfather)%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20screamed%20as%20I%20ran%20inside%20the%20house.%20His%20son%20was%20the%20unit%20Communist%20leader%20at%20that%20time.%20He%20was%20my%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20later%20when%20I%20realised%20how%20important%20he%20was%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20warmth%20he%20exuded%20irrespective%20of%20the%20age%20difference%20and%20how%20he%20had%20addressed%20everyone%20as%20a%20comrade.%20Whenever%20comrade%20Sankaraiah%20got%20down%20from%20a%20train%20and%20walked%20towards%20his%20house%2C%20I%20would%20stand%20on%20the%20road%20along%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20wish%20him%3A%20%E2%80%9CVanakkam%2C%20comrade.%E2%80%9D%20In%20response%2C%20he%20would%20also%20enthusiastically%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CVanakkam%20comrade%E2%80%99.%20As%20a%20student%2C%20this%20gesture%20left%20me%20with%20a%20great%20sense%20of%20excitement.%20I%20often%20stood%20on%20the%20road%20along%20with%20friends%20just%20for%20this%20moment.%20To%20me%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20great%20happiness%20that%20I%20understood%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20word%20comrade%20coming%20directly%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fn-sankaraiah-one-hundred-years-a-revolutionary%5C%22%3EN.%20Sankaraiah%3A%20One%20Hundred%20Years%20a%20Revolutionary%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComrade%20Sankaraiah%20was%20a%20disciplined%20human%20being.%20Even%20though%20he%20had%20many%20tasks%20and%20held%20many%20responsibilities%20in%20the%20Communist%20party%2C%20he%20would%20make%20a%20note%20of%20every%20event%20that%20he%20had%20to%20attend%20and%20go%20on%20time.%20I%20was%20always%20n%20in%20awe%20of%20his%20punctuality.%20He%20would%20never%20make%20anyone%20wait%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20a%20wedding%20event%20or%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20comrade%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Sankaraiah%20valued%20others%E2%80%99%20time%20as%20much%20as%20he%20valued%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%2097%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20travel%20with%20him%20for%20a%20conference%20in%20Madurai.%20He%20meticulously%20planned%20every%20detail%20about%20the%20trip.%20Right%20from%20enquiring%20about%20the%20train%20timings%20to%20where%20to%20have%20our%20meal%20and%20how%20to%20return%2C%20Sankaraiah%20never%20left%20anything%20to%20chance%20and%20made%20sure%20that%20I%20followed%20the%20same.%20When%20I%20met%20him%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20he%20was%20still%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20man%20behind%20the%20legend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComrade%20Sankariah%20is%20today%20known%20throughout%20the%20country%20as%20veteran%20leader%20of%20the%20Communist%20party.%20But%20had%20never%20let%20the%20fame%20to%20manifest%20in%20his%20personality.%20He%20was%20a%20leader%20nonpareil%20who%20only%20functioned%20under%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20orders.%20After%20stepping%20down%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20secretary%20in%202002%2C%20Sankaraiah%20would%20willingly%20accept%20any%20responsibility%20given%20by%20the%20party%20and%20worked%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20performance%20as%20the%20state%20secretary%20was%20impeccable.%20Even%20when%20people%20younger%20than%20him%20were%20in-charge%20of%20the%20party%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20resolutions%20had%20always%20been%20his%20charter.%20He%20never%20gave%20an%20interview%20to%20any%20media%20house%20without%20explicit%20approval%20of%20the%20party.%20Besides%2C%20he%20also%20regularly%20read%20all%20the%20statements%2C%20magazines%20and%20documents%20of%20the%20party.%20He%20kept%20himself%20abreast%20of%20all%20development%2C%20from%20local%20to%20global%2C%20and%20was%20extremely%20knowledgeable.%20He%20was%20also%20keen%20and%20sensitive%20enough%20to%20know%20about%20every%20struggle%20waged%20by%20the%20party.%20When%20I%20went%20to%20meet%20him%20last%20month%2C%20he%20enquired%20about%20the%20consequences%20of%20each%20stage%20of%20the%20actions%20the%20party%20had%20taken%20for%20recent%20forced%20evictions%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComrade%20Sankaraiah%20was%20fluent%20in%20English.%20Even%20as%20a%20student%2C%20comrade%20Sankaraiah%20would%20translate%20the%20speeches%20of%20leaders%20like%20P.%20C.%20Joshi%20(Communist%20Party%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20general%20secretary)%20and%20A.%20K.%20Gopalan%20into%20Tamil%20during%20their%20visits%20to%20the%20state.%20He%20was%20sharp%20enough%20to%20translate%20them%20into%20Tamil%20without%20even%20taking%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelf-awareness%20was%20a%20trait%20that%20comrade%20Sankaraiah%20had%20consciously%20developed%20for%20himself.%20He%20would%20never%20accept%20things%20that%20he%20did%20not%20find%20palatable.%20He%20exercised%20restraint%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20food%20and%20advised%20other%20comrades%20to%20do%20the%20same%20as%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20their%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESankaraiah%20was%20a%20leader%20who%20took%20pleasure%20and%20pride%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20leaders%20and%20gave%20way%20for%20them.%20Even%20though%20he%20would%20cut%20short%20his%20attendance%20to%20many%20public%20events%20for%20this%20reason%2C%20he%20would%20regularly%20send%20out%20congratulatory%20messages%20and%20articles%20by%20way%20of%20encouragement.%20Generations%20of%20Communist%20leaders%20are%20indebted%20to%20comrade%20Sankaraiah.%20Not%20just%20in%20the%20party%2C%20even%20in%20his%20own%20family%2C%20ever%20member%20was%20a%20Communist%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgainst%20caste%20and%20religion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20has%20seen%20weddings%20between%20members%20of%20all%20castes.%20Sankaraiah%20himself%20fell%20in%20love%20and%20married%20Navamani%20Ammal%2C%20a%20Christian%20and%20his%20fellow%20traveler%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20Their%20marriage%20was%20both%20inter-caste%20and%20inter-communal.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20such%20inter-caste%20and%20inter-religious%20marriages%20in%20his%20family.%20Sankaraiah%20had%20always%20encouraged%20the%20youth%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20and%20get%20married.%20His%20speeches%20against%20caste%20oppression%20instilled%20rationalism%20in%20the%20youth.%20He%20made%20sure%20that%20his%20own%20family%20followed%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20Communist%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Comrade%20Sankariah%20tested%20positive%20for%20covid%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Hospital%2C%20the%20way%20he%20faced%20the%20disease%20and%20the%20cooperated%20with%20the%20doctors%20was%20awe-inspiring.%20Perhaps%20his%20fighting%20spirit%20manifested%20itself%20against%20the%20disease%20even%20when%20he%20was%20100%20years%20old.%20Even%20this%20time%2C%20he%20struggled%20as%20much%20as%20he%20could%20against%20the%20disease.%20The%20Communist%20red%20sun%20that%20had%20lived%20an%20admirable%20public%20life%2C%20remained%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20Communist%20party%20till%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EG.%20Selva%20is%20the%20CPI%20(M)%20Central%20Chennai%20district%20secretary.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700381974000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19134216%2FN.Sankaraiah_CPIM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fan-ode-to-the-101-year-old-freedom-fighter-and-communist-n-sankaraiah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20lived%20an%20admirable%20public%20life%20and%20remained%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20Communist%20party%20till%20the%20end.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fan-ode-to-the-101-year-old-freedom-fighter-and-communist-n-sankaraiah%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22