%20create%20a%20planter%20that%20is%20both%20simple%20and%20optimised.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20my%20design%20to%20be%20fascinating%20for%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAwarded%20for%20%E2%80%98designing%20for%20a%20better%20tomorrow%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20appreciation%20from%20the%20jury%2C%20Gowtham%20launched%20this%20product%20under%20the%20brand%20%E2%80%98Floraqua%E2%80%99%20on%20Facebook.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20students%20do%20not%20take%20their%20college-level%20projects%20forward.%20They%20get%20occupied%20in%20the%20next%20semester%20or%20get%20a%20job.%20I%20wanted%20to%20market%20this%20project%20so%20that%20people%20can%20use%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202018%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20Experiencing%20Live%20Action%20Business%20Course%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20(IIM)%20Ahmedabad%20to%20learn%20entrepreneurship.%20%E2%80%9CIIMA%E2%80%99s%20team%20approved%20the%20product.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20course%2C%20I%20began%20creating%20different%20versions%20of%20the%20planter%2C%20and%20the%20team%20would%20handle%20its%20sales%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gowtham%2C%20who%20works%20with%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20interior%20designer%20company%2C%20MIPL%20Global.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20integrated%20the%20famous%20Rajasthani%20Molela%20craft%20into%20my%20design%20at%20the%20rim%20of%20the%20pot%20to%20give%20the%20planter%20an%20aesthetic%20appeal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Priced%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20Gowatham%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20nearly%20300%20planters%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20team%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-1700051764.jpg%5C%22%20width